reviews.review: Great movie entertainment. Fun and good closure to the series.
you could definitely tell that they did not have a plan for how the series would end.
terrible acting. didn't feel the drama.  some nice callbacks to the original trilogy though.
Still a missed opportunity but miles better than TLJ. Miles better. I actually warmed to the new heroes, whereas I couldn't be doing with them in RJ's terrible film.

Loved the OT, PT has grown on me hugely(mostly) I loved TFA, loved lots about TLJ but a couple of things still really grate. Seen TROS and thought it was great - not without fault but great! Just had my second viewing and loved it more!

Overall a good popcorn movie. Start felt a little more like a montage but it improved. They were obviously trying to fix the plot from the last movie. Critics will hate on it because it has to undo the last film which they defend heavily and super starwars fans will because it had to mangle the lore and had some plot holes (its effectively two movies in one) but the general public will like it
This movie is pure trash! Wouldnâ€™t surprise me if Disney were paying for these reviews. Was glad to see that the critics got the movie scores right.

I finished watching the movie and it's one of the worst things I ever have seen, it pretty much makes all the sacrifices of Anakin and Luke meaningless in the end. I truly don't understand how they could just end the Skywalker bloodline like this, it's a massive pass for me and I won't go back and watch this

this just gives me more reasons to care about the old eps 1 through 6 and the EU, this movie is terrible.

The best it could be after the damage Rian Johnson caused by destroying everything that JJ Abrams setup. Outstanding visuals and soundtrack. 

This is the Tron Legacy of the Star Wars franchise. Not perfect but a great experience none the less.

Spoiler free. Best movie since empire strikes back. This is the disconnect between critics and fans. Most of us thought the last jedi was bad at best. The complaint about this movie seems to be the nostalgia. That's the coolest part of this movie. In my opinion this movie righted the wrong path that the last jedi went down and in a way actually made that movie better in the process.
